Have a Ball at the Lanes
A transformative space, Cordova Lanes is perfect for your next special event! Our space is totally customizable to your needs. We host wedding receptions, fundraisers, family reunions, and more. We can host events and parties with up to 350 guests. Contact us to get the ball rolling!
